    public class DelimitedTextTableReader
extends TextFileTableReader<java.lang.String[]>
    The DelimitedTextTableReader class allows data tables to be read from delimited data text files. Internally, the class uses a DelimitedDataReader with the specified delimiter, so the parsing rules set out in that class apply to table files read by this class.
    See Also:
    DelimitedDataReader
